Title: 调用关系
Describe: 展示系统中三条核心调用链：LLM 调用链（入口→重试→API）、工具分发链（model→hook→handler→result）、团队通信链（lead→bus→teammate→protocol）。
------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
LLM 调用链

[Description]
从用户输入到 LLM API 调用的完整调用路径：

```
__main__ → agent_loop() → call_llm() → with_retry() → client.messages.create()
```

涉及的关键函数：
- `agent_loop` (L1901): 主循环入口
- `call_llm` (L1888): 组装 system prompt + 调用
- `with_retry` (L1167): 重试包装器
- `assemble_system_prompt` (L359): 构建系统提示
- `client.messages.create`: Anthropic API

[UML]
@startuml
participant "CLI (__main__)" as cli
participant "agent_loop" as loop
participant "prepare_context" as prep
participant "call_llm" as call
participant "with_retry" as retry
participant "assemble_system_prompt" as asm
participant "Anthropic API" as api

cli -> loop : agent_loop(history, context)
activate loop

loop -> prep : prepare_context(messages)
activate prep
prep -> prep : tool_result_budget()
prep -> prep : snip_compact()
prep -> prep : micro_compact()
prep --> loop : messages (压缩后)
deactivate prep

loop -> call : call_llm(messages, context, tools, state, max_tokens)
activate call
call -> asm : assemble_system_prompt(context)
asm --> call : system prompt string
call -> retry : with_retry(lambda, state)
activate retry
retry -> api : client.messages.create(\n  model, system, messages, tools, max_tokens)
api --> retry : response
retry --> call : response
deactivate retry
call --> loop : response
deactivate call

loop --> cli : 返回 (循环结束时)
deactivate loop
@enduml

[Detail]
调用链的每一层都有明确职责：`agent_loop` 负责循环控制和错误处理策略；`call_llm` 负责 prompt 组装；`with_retry` 负责重试逻辑和模型降级；`assemble_system_prompt` 负责将动态上下文（memory、skills、MCP 状态）编入提示。这种分层使得修改重试策略不影响 prompt 组装逻辑。

------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
工具分发链

[Description]
当 LLM 返回 tool_use 时的完整分发路径：

```
response.content → for block → PreToolUse hook → handler(**args) → PostToolUse hook → tool_result
```

关键分支：
- `compact` → 直接调用 `compact_history`，break 跳出
- Hook 拒绝 → 返回 "Permission denied" 作为 result
- Background → `start_background_task`，返回 placeholder
- 正常 → `handlers[name](**args)`

[UML]
@startuml
participant "agent_loop" as loop
participant "Hook Pipeline" as hooks
participant "permission_hook" as perm
participant "log_hook" as log
participant "Background" as bg
participant "Tool Handler" as handler
participant "large_output_hook" as loh

loop -> loop : block = response.content[i] (tool_use)
loop -> hooks : trigger_hooks("PreToolUse", block)
activate hooks
hooks -> perm : permission_hook(block)
alt 被拒绝
  perm --> hooks : "Permission denied: ..."
  hooks --> loop : blocked result
else 允许
  perm --> hooks : None
  hooks -> log : log_hook(block)
  log --> hooks : None
  hooks --> loop : None (允许执行)
end
deactivate hooks

alt should_run_background
  loop -> bg : start_background_task(block, handlers)
  bg --> loop : bg_id placeholder
else 同步执行
  loop -> handler : handlers[block.name](**block.input)
  handler --> loop : output string
  loop -> hooks : trigger_hooks("PostToolUse", block, output)
  hooks -> loh : large_output_hook(block, output)
  loh --> hooks : None
  hooks --> loop : None
end

loop -> loop : results.append(tool_result)
@enduml

[Detail]
Hook 管道的执行是**短路**模式：PreToolUse 中任何 hook 返回非 None 值都会立即停止执行链。这意味着 `permission_hook` 排在第一位——如果权限被拒绝，`log_hook` 都不会被调用。PostToolUse 的 `large_output_hook` 只做监控告警，不阻止结果返回。

------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
团队通信链

[Description]
Lead Agent 与 Teammate 之间的 Plan Approval 协议完整交互：

1. Lead 调用 `spawn_teammate(name, role, prompt)` 创建 Teammate
2. Teammate 工作中调用 `submit_plan(plan)` 提交计划
3. Lead 通过 `check_inbox` 看到 plan_approval_request
4. Lead 调用 `review_plan(request_id, approve, feedback)` 审批
5. Teammate 收到 plan_approval_response，继续或修改

[UML]
@startuml
participant "Lead (agent_loop)" as lead
participant "MessageBus" as bus
participant "Teammate Thread" as tm
participant "ProtocolState" as proto

== 创建 Teammate ==
lead -> tm : spawn_teammate_thread(name, role, prompt)
activate tm
tm -> tm : 启动 daemon Thread

== Teammate 工作 ==
tm -> tm : LLM 循环执行工具

== 提交计划 ==
tm -> proto : _teammate_submit_plan(name, plan)
proto -> proto : 创建 ProtocolState(type="plan_approval")
tm -> bus : BUS.send(name, "lead", plan,\n  "plan_approval_request", {request_id})
tm -> tm : protocol_ctx["waiting_plan"] = req_id
note right of tm : 进入等待循环\n(只轮询 inbox)

== Lead 审批 ==
lead -> bus : consume_lead_inbox()
bus --> lead : [{type: "plan_approval_request", ...}]
lead -> lead : 展示计划给用户/模型
lead -> bus : run_review_plan(req_id, True, "")
bus -> tm : BUS.send("lead", name, "Approved",\n  "plan_approval_response", {approve: True})

== Teammate 恢复 ==
tm -> tm : handle_inbox_message() 收到响应
tm -> tm : protocol_ctx["waiting_plan"] = None
tm -> tm : messages.append("[Plan approved]")
tm -> tm : 继续 LLM 循环
deactivate tm
@enduml

[Detail]
Plan Approval Gate 是 s20 中最复杂的协议交互。关键机制：(1) `protocol_ctx["waiting_plan"]` 作为阻塞标记——设置后 Teammate 只轮询 inbox，不调用 LLM；(2) `match_response` 通过 `request_id` 严格匹配——shutdown_response 不会被误解为 plan approval；(3) Lead 端的 `consume_lead_inbox(route_protocol=True)` 自动路由协议消息到 `pending_requests`。

------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
Cron 注入链

[Description]
从 Cron 表达式匹配到 Agent 执行的完整链路：

```
cron_scheduler_loop → cron_matches → cron_queue.append
→ agent_loop.consume_cron_queue → messages.append → LLM 处理
```

两条注入路径：
- **主循环内注入**: `agent_loop` 每轮开始时 `consume_cron_queue()`
- **自动执行注入**: `cron_autorun_loop` 在用户空闲时独立触发

[UML]
@startuml
participant "cron_scheduler_loop\n(daemon thread)" as sched
participant "cron_queue\n(shared list)" as queue
participant "agent_loop\n(main thread)" as loop
participant "cron_autorun_loop\n(daemon thread)" as auto
participant "LLM" as llm

== 调度器每秒检查 ==
sched -> sched : now = datetime.now()
sched -> sched : cron_matches(job.cron, now)
sched -> queue : cron_queue.append(job)
sched -> sched : _last_fired[job.id] = marker

== 路径1: 主循环注入 ==
loop -> queue : consume_cron_queue()
queue --> loop : [fired_jobs]
loop -> loop : messages.append("[Scheduled] {prompt}")
loop -> llm : call_llm(messages, ...)

== 路径2: 自动执行注入 ==
auto -> queue : consume_cron_queue()
queue --> auto : [fired_jobs]
auto -> auto : history.append("[Scheduled] {prompt}")
auto -> loop : agent_loop(history, context)
note right: 需要 acquire agent_lock
@enduml

[Detail]
双路径注入设计解决了"用户不输入时 Cron 任务是否执行"的问题：`cron_autorun_loop` 确保即使用户没有输入，Cron 触发的任务也会被执行。`_last_fired` 字典以分钟为粒度去重，防止同一分钟内重复触发。`agent_lock` 确保主线程的 `agent_loop` 和自动执行的 `agent_loop` 不会并发运行。
